If you want to find out the percent-match between two multiple-response questions, here is the solution.

q1<- "hh-0 & hh-2 & hh-3"
q2<- "hh-0 & hh-3 & hh-5"

map2(
  str_split(q1, " & "),
  str_split(q2, " & "),
  ~sum(.x %in% .y)/length(.x)
)
